{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_01","textHome":"轻轻斩落你的心！@恋之试刀公主，史乃沙优希，参上~的说！@……啊呜！弄、弄错了……@这里不是舞台呀~那、那就，重来一遍，@史乃沙优希！喜欢刀和围绕着刀的历史~@请多多关照！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_17","textHome":"在雷击当中守护名将立花道雪殿下，@从而得名的雷切丸，@让人感觉像守护神一般可靠~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_18","textHome":"织田信长殿下、丰臣秀吉殿下……@然后是德川家康殿下。@宗三左文字就是流转于著名的三英杰之手的，@一把富有魅力的刀哦~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_19","textHome":"作为魔法少女，或是作为偶像都成长了呢~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_20","textHome":"啊哇！又学到了一个新的阶段呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_21","textHome":"做过各种各样的工作~@还是觉得……演唱会最好啦~@能和大家一起分享感动，是很宝贵的时间！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_22","textHome":"虽然是歌唱和舞蹈都菜菜的沙优希…… @但有一件事是不会输给别的偶像的~@那就是和大家的羁绊~@大家都像真正的朋友一样暖心~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_23","textHome":"不只是沙优希把元气分给大家~@也不只是大家把元气借给沙优希~@而是大家一起，创造出让人欢笑的空间来……@沙优希想成为这样的偶像！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_24","textHome":"遇上我就是你的末日，想被如何斩杀呢~@……呜喵！？什么时候来的！？@不、不是要斩你啦~只是在练习开场白！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":1}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_25","textHome":"哈~清爽的早晨！早饭也要好好吃！@白米饭……味噌汤……还有酱菜……@吃饱了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_26","textHome":"哈呜~肚子饿了……@不介意的话，午饭想一起吃，的说！@哈哇！辣、辣的东西吃不了……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_02","textHome":"啊哇！初次会面！@沙优希……全名是史乃沙优希！@虽然不太起眼，但有在做水名区的本地偶像！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_27","textHome":"戴克……里……@哈哇~有点记不住了……@超过五个片假名就……哈呜……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_28","textHome":"还不钻进被窝的吗？@半夜三更不睡的话，会有长舌老妖婆出来哦。@爷爷是这样告诉沙优希的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_29","textHome":"有空的话，一起来读@沙优希这本《刀剑大全之历史》吧~@上面写了好多刀的资料，解说和照片都很棒，@是梦幻般的好书哦~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_30","textHome":"哈哇！该去消灭魔女了的说~@沙优希没有二话！职责就要认真完成！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_31","textHome":"呜~紧张得肚子痛……在街道上都会迷路了，@何况全是镜子的洋馆呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_32","textHome":"来人！来人出战！@……哎。就算沙优希生在江户时代，@肯定也不适合做那种打头阵的武士的说~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_33","textHome":"日本刀真是绝妙~其美丽无需多言，@一把把……都充盈着历史与浪漫~@哇……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_34","textHome":"经纪人小姐帮沙优希想的口号是@「恋之试刀公主」……@可试刀的人不是很危险的那种人么……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_35","textHome":"小时候，我就很喜欢唱歌~@就是……合唱的时候，@总是被喊说不要唱那么大声……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_36","textHome":"新曲的歌词是，@被所仰慕的男生说出讨厌的，女孩子的故事。@哇~年轻的女孩好难呀……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_03","textHome":"啊嘞？本来只是想听听的……@沙优希就这么签下去了……？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":300}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_37","textHome":"不像兔子也不像猫……@丘比真是奇妙的动物~@啊哇！难道说……是妖狐么！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":300}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_38","textHome":"沙优希的粉丝们把沙优希叫做“沙优沙优”。@诶嘿，有个外号真好~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_39","textHome":"因为决定要做沙优希的印象荧光棒了，@想请厂家做成打刀的大小，@结果被否决了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_40","textHome":"休息日，经常和麻友一起去美术馆和博物馆~@去看刀和画的说~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":200}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3033_00_41","textHome":"哈！呀！哦！……啊啊啊……噗！@呜~又自己绊倒了……@沙优希虽然喜欢刀剑……@可是剑术完全不行……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303300}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_